---
title: Glazed Bacon-Wrapped Pork with Fresh Peach Salsa and Creamy Potato Salad
description: Peach season is here! A juicy peach salsa is fresh and delightful paired with bacon-wrapped pork roast in a sweet and smoky glaze. The side is no side piece: this loaded potato salad is reminiscent of sour cream and onion chips!
